              	&lt;p class="mb-0 opacity-75 lead text-muted"&gt;&lt;b&gt;In Short:&lt;/b&gt;  Some information — such as your Internet Protocol (IP) address and/or browser and device characteristics — is collected automatically when you visit our App.
